1. ID: `F-01`
   Severity: HIGH
   Category: code-bug
   Evidence: [计划]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md#L220 )把 `completed -> published` 加进 `_VALID_STATUS_TRANSITIONS`，并且测试直接通过 `update_exam(..., status="published")` 走状态变更入口（[计划]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md#L159 )、[计划]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md#L265 )）；但现有 `PATCH /api/v1/exams/{exam_id}` 仅依赖 `get_current_user`，没有 `MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS` 或发布专用校验（[router]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py#L111 )、[router]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py#L116 )）。设计又明确要求 `completed -> published` 先过前置条件（[设计]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-design.md#L95 )）。
   Impact: 任何能调 `PATCH /exams/{id}` 的调用方都可以绕过发布权限、质量阻塞和发布流水线，直接把考试置为 `published`。这是 Tier-1 风险。
   Suggested action: 禁止 `update_exam()` 处理 `published/archived`，这两个状态只能经 `ExamPublishService.publish/archive` 进入；同时给专用端点强制 `require_permission(Permission.MANAGE_EXAM_RESULTS)`。

2. ID: `F-02`
   Severity: HIGH
   Category: code-bug
   Evidence: 计划中的 `ExamPublishService.publish/archive` 直接 `db.get(Exam, exam_id)`，没有校验 `exam.school_id == school_id`（[计划]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md#L977 )、[计划]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.1-exam-workflow-plan.md#L1008 )）；而现有考试读取基线是按 `exam_id + school_id` 双条件查询（[service]( /C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/service.py#L41 )）。
   Impact: 只要知道别校 `exam_id`，就可能跨校发布/归档考试；即使 API 层传了当前学校 `school_id`，服务层仍不会拦截。这是多租户越权风险。
   Suggested action: `publish/archive` 必须复用现有 `get_exam(db, exam_id, school_id)`，或至少在读到实体后显式校验 `exam.school_id`。

